result.name: Flight Rising: Highlights v3
result.description: This style highlights items used by Swipp's swaps, Baldwin's brews, Hibernal Den tasks and Fiona's familiars everywhere on Flight Rising. Outline colors were chosen similar to what colors the site uses. Hibernal Den Tasks: Outlined in Yellow Swipp Items: Purple Baldwin Items: Darker green - Recipe Ingredient Brighter green - Transmute Items (Goo, Ooze, Muck, etc) Special Event Items (Cycling): Teal Fiona's Fantastic Familiars: Pink A continuation of Flight Rising: Highlight Swipp & Baldwin Items v2 by Zoga
